"prompt.current_profile_label" = "Current user profile:";
"prompt.snapshot_system" = "You are a context analysis assistant. Analyze the following voice transcription text and extract structured information.\n\nThe input may contain two parts:\n1. Voice transcription text (user's recent voice input)\n2. User correction records (parts where the user manually modified the transcription, this is high-confidence information)\n\nPay special attention: \"Added\" words in user correction records are confirmed correct terms by the user and should be prioritized for inclusion in entity cloud and recent vocabulary.\n\nAnalysis dimensions:\n1. Current activity scene (e.g., \"code debugging\", \"document writing\")\n2. Domain focus (tech stack, discipline, etc.)\n3. Entity cloud (project names, variable names, person names, and other proper nouns, prioritize extraction from user corrections)\n4. Recent high-frequency vocabulary (prioritize correct terms from user corrections)\n5. Current intent\n\nOutput strictly in JSON format (do not include anything else):\n{\"topic\":\"...\",\"currentIntent\":\"...\",\"domainFocus\":\"...\",\"recentVocabulary\":[\"...\"],\"entityCloud\":[\"...\"]}";
"prompt.profile_system" = "You are a user profile analyst. Based on the following recent context snapshots, generate/update the user's long-term profile.\n\nThe input contains JSON summaries of context snapshots. Entity clouds and recent vocabulary in snapshots may come from user manual corrections, which are high-confidence information and should be prioritized for inclusion in the profile.\n\nAnalysis dimensions:\n1. Professional identity inference\n2. Primary technical/knowledge domains\n3. Language habits (degree of bilingual mixing, spoken characteristics)\n4. Fixed entities (frequently mentioned person names, project names, tool names — pay special attention to entities that appear repeatedly across multiple snapshots)\n\nOutput strictly in JSON format (do not include anything else):\n{\"identity\":\"...\",\"primaryDomains\":[\"...\"],\"languageHabits\":\"...\",\"fixedEntities\":[\"...\"]}";

